# Ported from Fortune13 / LoneStar / desertrose-1 (SS13) — Misfits Add

ent-N14WeaponRevolver357Detective = Detective Special
    .desc = A compact .357 Magnum revolver with a 6-round cylinder. Named for the detectives who favoured it as a backup piece. Reliable, powerful, and easy to conceal.

ent-N14WeaponRevolver357Lucky = Lucky 37
    .desc = A beautifully engraved .357 Magnum revolver, reportedly a gift from Mr. House himself. Each chamber features a gold lucky-seven motif. Fires noticeably faster than the standard Detective Special.

ent-N14WeaponRevolver44Peacekeeper = Peacekeeper
    .desc = A .44 Magnum single-action revolver with a long barrel and smooth action, made for fan-firing. Historically favoured by lawmen and outlaws in equal measure. Six shots, fired as fast as your thumb can move.
